    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"useref-vs-usestate-차이점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useref-vs-usestate-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"useref vs usestate 차이점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useRef vs useState 차이점</h1>\n<h2 id=\"usestate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usestate\" aria-label=\"usestate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useState</h2>\n<p>useState는 setState에 의해 값이 변경되면, 렌더링을 새로하여 화면에 보여준다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"useref\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useref\" aria-label=\"useref permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useRef</h2>\n<p>반면 useRef는 값을 변경하더라도 렌더링을 하지 않아 메모리적인 측면에서 가볍다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>useRef는 DOM을 조작할 때 사용하기도 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"결론\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EB%A1%A0\" aria-label=\"결론 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결론</h2>\n<p>화면에 나타내는 값이 아니라면 상황에 따라 useRef 혹은 일반 변수 선언을 통해 사용하면 될 것이며, 화면에 나타나는 값이라면 useState를 사용하면 된다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"useRef vs useState 차이점","date":"23 August, 2021"},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#useref-vs-usestate-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\">useRef vs useState 차이점</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#usestate\">useState</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#useref\">useRef</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EB%A1%A0\">결론</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/useRef-vs-useState/"}},
